OL,6,F"It has been an absolute joy and
OL,7,Fprivilege to present such an iconic
OL,8,Fshow for the BBC, but all things have
OL,9,Fto come to an end," Lineker said on
OL,10,Fhis podcast, The Rest Is Football.
OL,12,F"It came at a point where really the
OL,13,FBBC and Match Of The Day, they've got
OL,14,Fthe rights for another three years,
OL,15,Fthe cycle starts from next season so
OL,16,Fit felt like if I just do one more
OL,17,Fyear it would be a bit weird."
