OL,6,FThe Leciester-born sports presenter
OL,7,Fadded: "I bowed out in my football
OL,8,Fcareer when I felt it was the right
OL,9,Ftime. I feel this is now the right
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"I think the next contract they're
OL,13,Flooking to do Match Of The Day
OL,14,Fslightly differently, so I think it
OL,15,Fmakes sense for someone else to take
OL,16,Fthe helm."
