OL,6,FHowever, Lineker did not speculate on
OL,7,Fwho would replace him on MOTD. Rumours
OL,8,Fhave cast Mark Chapman, the regular
OL,9,FMatch Of The Day 2 presenter, Football
OL,10,FFocus host Alex Scott, and BBC sports
OL,11,Fcoverage presenter Gabby Logan, as
OL,12,Fpotential replacements.
OL,14,F"Obviously I don't know who it'll be,
OL,15,Fand I would never tell publicly my
OL,16,Fpreference, I don't think that'd be
OL,17,Fthe right thing to do ` but whoever it
OL,18,Fis, I would say be yourself," he said.
OL,20,F"I had to fill the ginormous shoes of
OL,21,Fcertain Des Lynam.
