OL,6,F"...I would say just be yourself and
OL,7,Fenjoy it, it's a wonderful programme
OL,8,Fto be a part of. It was brilliant
OL,9,Fbefore I took over, and it will be
OL,10,Fbrilliant after I leave.
OL,12,FSince 1999, Lineker has hosted MOTD
OL,13,Fand will have presented the show for
OL,14,Fmore than a quarter of a century when
OL,15,Fhe leaves in May 2025.
OL,17,FHe said: "I look back and it's been an
OL,18,Famazing experience, and I feel
OL,19,Fincredibly fortunate."
