OL,6,FLast year, Lineker was briefly
OL,7,Fsuspended from hosting MOTD after his
OL,8,Ftweet about the Tory government's
OL,9,FRwanda policy ignited controversy
OL,10,Fregarding BBC's presenters expressing
OL,11,Fpolitical opinions on social media.
OL,13,F"I've had a lot of chaos over the last
OL,14,Fcouple of years in many ways," Lineker
OL,15,Fjoked, saying he was on "first-name
OL,16,Fterms with some of the people that
OL,17,Fstand outside my front door".
