OL,6,FHe added that he was surprised by "the
OL,7,Famount of love" he has received since
OL,8,Fnews of his departure broke, which he
OL,9,Fdescribed as "a bit bonkers".
OL,11,F"I didn't think it would be quite the
OL,12,Fbig deal that it was ` it's just a guy
OL,13,Fthat has done a TV show for a long
OL,14,Ftime, it's nothing more than," he said.
OL,16,FLineker will continue hosting the MOTD
OL,17,FTop Ten podcast, while his other
OL,18,Fpodcast, The Rest is Football,
OL,19,Ffeaturing BBC pundits Alan Shearer and
OL,20,FMicah Richards, will now be available
OL,21,Fon BBC Sounds.
